; Compute 5! = 120 using recursion.
; MEM[0] stores the child result while the current frame restores its saved n.
; 11 cells is the smallest stack that safely fits the full call tree for n = 5.
.memory 11

LOADI 5
CALL fact
HALT

fact:
JZ fact_base
PUSH
SUB 1
CALL fact
STORE 0
POP
MULM 0
RET

fact_base:
LOADI 1
RET
